Everyone else is there so you don&#39;t get Frodo killed.<br />
<br />
SHADOW:<br />
<br />
This Minions are what keep this deck going.  I am thinking of switching to a Uruk discard...but the Uruk&#39;s I am playing now kill real good.  No joke.  They smash and crash.  Take control of site&#39;s and throw down with nasty conditions.  I think 3 or 4 Saruman, KoI are too much, I might add Servant of the Eye instead of more KoI.<br />
<br />
